{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972310/extras/titleGifMain3.gif?t=1737567634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972310/extras/YouAreTheHerald.png?t=1737567634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as the Queen's Herald and immerse yourself in a <strong>text-based RPG</strong> full of choices and dice rolls. Interact with a diverse cast of characters, each with their own stories to tell and secrets to uncover. Navigate a web of alliances and rivalries as you forge relationships with factions and people throughout The Mists.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972310/extras/AWorldHidden.png?t=1737567634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Queen\u2019s army is gone, and The Mists hold the answers. Embark on an\u00a0<strong>adventure</strong> <strong>through a mist-shrouded world</strong> and uncover the secrets hidden behind it. Dive into the depths of intrigue and betrayal as you navigate a realm where nothing is as it seems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972310/extras/ForgeYourPath.png?t=1737567634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shape your destiny through your <strong>choices and actions</strong>. Become a cunning rogue, a masterful mage, a fearless warrior, or something uniquely your own. You are travelling all the time, so what you decide to carry with yourself is equally important. Your decisions will carve your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972310/extras/OldSchool.png?t=1737567634\" /><